General.Name: Z.M.H Hammerman Ltd
General.Description: Z.M.H Hammerman Ltd operates as a construction company in Israel. It mainly engages in the initiation and execution of residential, office, and commercial projects, as well as in the execution of other projects for companies. The company was incorporated in 1997 and is based in Hadera, Israel.
